# Backend Testing

## API test coverage

- Every API/server function file must have a corresponding unit test file next to it.
- Prefer colocated naming, for example:
  - `src/server/health/ping.ts`
  - `src/server/health/ping.test.ts`

## Rule intent

- Changes to backend API behavior should include or update the colocated unit tests in the same area.
